bus device driver

bus can match device and driver

when registe device and driver, need struct bus_type that defined in bus,
so you shoud:
cat bus/Module.symvers > device/Module.symvers
cat bus/Module.symvers > driver/Module.symvers
to avoid warning in make and error(module have undefined symbol).

